// --- BUBBLER+ STARTUP SCRIPT ---

// 1. Define the Laws
set.[PLAYER.SPEED.25]
set.[WORLD.GRAVITY.15]

// 2. Create the World
construct.[BASEPLATE.SIZE.100, 1, 100]
modify.[BASEPLATE.COLOR.DARK_GRAY]

// 3. Add a Fun Element
construct.[BOUNCE_PAD.SIZE.5, 1, 5]
place.[BOUNCE_PAD.TO. 0, 1, 10]
modify.[BOUNCE_PAD.COLOR.NEON_BLUE]

// 4. Link the Logic
on.[TOUCH.BOUNCE_PAD] >> launch.[PLAYER.UP.60]
